originalText.text: I’ve been getting facials here since COVID. My esthetician who was amazing left the country and recommended Carmel—who trained her on microcurrent. Carmel and the Environ products give lifting, firming results. I need collagen building at 49 yo and she does not disappoint. Today I had my first microcurrent treatment finally w Carmel and I already booked my next in a few weeks. My deep 11’s are gone as is the deep furrow above my eye, which is unbelievable. I stopped Botox over a year ago and as far as what I see, I won’t need it under Carmel’s regimen.
